title: Check Out Rajkummar Rao Starrer Trapped’s New Poster
text:
tweet Here’s presenting the brand new poster of the upcoming movie Trapped . The poster features Rajkummar Rao playing the character called Shaurya. The film revolves around an interesting tale of survival where a man is trapped in a house for days without food and water. 
Check out the poster here: Trapped Movie Poster The trailer of the movie will be out on 22nd February. Directed by Vikramaditya Motwane, the film is slated to release on 17th March. TAGS
